title: Sufjan Stevens - Live @ Lee's Palace
description:
This is a soundboard bootleg I found on archive.org. I split the tracks up in audacity and tagged them appropriately.

There are a few glitches (which occurred with the source), but the set is DEFINITELY worth listening to.

The live versions of &#039;Sister&#039;, &#039;Chicago&#039; and &#039;Super Sexy Woman&#039; are EPIC.

Includes stories & dialog by Sufjan between songs.
